description: Describes the target networks associated with the specified Client VPN endpoint.

parameters.name: ClientVpnEndpointId
parameters.description: The ID of the Client VPN endpoint.

parameters.name: AssociationIds
parameters.description: The IDs of the target network associations. (string) ---

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: One or more filters. Filter names and values are case-sensitive. association-id - The ID of the association. target-network-id - The ID of the subnet specified as the target network. vpc-id - The ID of the VPC in which the target network is located. (dict) --- A filter name and value pair that is used to return a more specific list of results from a describe operation. Filters can be used to match a set of resources by specific criteria, such as tags, attributes, or IDs. If you specify multiple filters, the filters are joined with an AND, and the request returns only results that match all of the specified filters. For more information, see List and filter using the CLI and API in the Amazon EC2 User Guide. Name (string) --- The name of the filter. Filter names are case-sensitive. Values (list) --- The filter values. Filter values are case-sensitive. If you specify multiple values for a filter, the values are joined with an OR, and the request returns all results that match any of the specified values. (string) ---

nested_items.name: ClientVpnTargetNetworks
nested_items.description: Information about the associated target networks.

nested_items.name: VpcId
nested_items.description: The ID of the VPC in which the target network (subnet) is located.

nested_items.name: TargetNetworkId
nested_items.description: The ID of the subnet specified as the target network.

nested_items.name: ClientVpnEndpointId
nested_items.description: The ID of the Client VPN endpoint with which the target network is associated.

nested_items.name: Code
nested_items.description: The state of the target network association.

nested_items.name: Message
nested_items.description: A message about the status of the target network association, if applicable.

nested_items.name: SecurityGroups
nested_items.description: The IDs of the security groups applied to the target network association.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to use to retrieve the next page of results. This value is null when there are no more results to return.
